<p>Notes:</p>
<ol>
    <li>The <b>bolded files</b> are required by the platform.</li>
    <li>The <span class="text-success">green files</span> are files related to similarity search.</li>
    <li>The <b class="text-success">bolded green files</b> are required to run similarity search.</li>
    <li>The <b class="text-danger">bolded red files</b> are required to run machine learning prediction.</li>
    <li>The <b class="text-primary">bolded blue files</b> are required to run docking.</li>
    <li>The <b class="text-warning">bolded yellow files</b> are required to visualize.</li>
</ol>

